<br>
Next I went to Mines of Torgiran.  You have to go to the bottom of this place past a brigde that extends over a large lava pit.  Really cool looking.  Go down the tunnels and in rooms you will find Luggards(Anarcist, Occultist...and a few other melee ones).  Some of them HT, so be careful.  You will need a group for this.  I am an epic mage and with me I had another lvl 60 mage, 60 Shammy, 61 Druid, and a 65 Chanter.<br>
<br>
With that group we killed everything with ease.  After clearing a lot of crap and Luggards, one stone dropped.  Stones are called &quot;Strength of Lava&quot;.  You need 3 of these and return them to Vera in Gulf of Gunthak for the Elemental Empathy spell.  Right now I only have 1 of the stones.  I will go back with groups until I get the other 2.<br>
<br>
<br>
Good Luck to you all.<br>
<br>
Dafier Furor<br>
60 Epic Arch Mage<br>
